<a name="develbook"></a>
<h3><font color="#660000">Write some chapters for the Developers Handbook</font></h3>
    <p><b>Responsible:</b>
     &lt;<a href="mailto:doc@FreeBSD.org">doc@FreeBSD.org</a>&gt;</p>

     <p><b>Synopsis:</b></p>
    <ul>
    <li>The FreeBSD Developers Handbook is lacking in content, please help
